{
  "stem": "2578.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this is roll number two.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I could bring an example to illustrate just what I said a while ago.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In September of 1990-- of September, 1942, an order came from the German authorities to the Lodz ghetto that they need, I think, either 5,000 or 10,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All those who are over, I think, the age of 45 or 50, all those who are sick, and children up to about 8 or 10 years.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember the details, but more or less this was the request.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Naturally, everybody knew that these people are not going to work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and since we knew from the rumors of the past two years, we realized that these people are going to be killed somewhere, someplace.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the Jews decided not to obey this order.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the Judenrat decided not to do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Germans themselves came in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they ordered a curfew for eight days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "No one was allowed to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "No one was allowed to leave their houses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They came in, and they cordoned off a square block of homes, and they ordered all the people to go-- to come down to the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They ordered the Jewish police that went with them to go from room to room and look for people that are hiding, if they were hiding.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Whoever was hiding was shot on the spot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And those who were still in the rooms will-- had to-- they were moved down to the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were assembled in the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the-- the Germans would select small children, elderly, and sickly-looking people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were moved out from the courtyard into the streets, where trucks were waiting.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were loaded on the trucks and moved to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
